devdoc.details: A smart contract that allows users to take loans on their abstract positions, which are managed by the FactoryContract. Loans are granted in USDC and the contract collects interest from borrowers. The interest rate is updated periodically and depends on the total amount of liquidity provided by lenders and the amount of loans currently taken.
